    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of high-revving Bavarian engineering, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically pristine, this unit has undergone a comprehensive preventative maintenance suite, including a dual-unit VANOS overhaul, rod bearing replacement with treated shells, and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural rigidity. Power is managed via a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a variable M differential lock, providing unparalleled tactile feedback. The exterior retains its factory depth with original paint, while the interior features immaculate Nappa leather and a tight, rattle-free cockpit. This is an analog masterpiece, offering a linear torque curve and a visceral exhaust note that remains the benchmark for the ultimate driving machine.",
